{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LeWsfRE2PCegvrqJ2RaRcE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary of Convex Backend Files\n\n### **app/convex/users.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`get`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ id: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Object with filtered fields: `{ _id, username, displayName, avatarUrl }` or `null`\n   - **Auth:** None required (public read)\n\n2. **`getByUsername`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ username: v.string() }`\n   - **Returns:** Full user document (no filtering shown) or `null` (uses `.unique()`)\n   - **Auth:** None required\n   - **Index:** `by_username`\n\n3. **`getCurrentUser`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{}` (no arguments)\n   - **Returns:** Full user document or `null`\n   - **Auth:** Required (checks `ctx.auth.getUserIdentity()`)\n   - **Behavior:** Returns authenticated user's data via token identifier\n\n4. **`updateProfile`** (mutation)\n   - **Args:** `{ displayName?: v.string(), bio?: v.string(), avatarUrl?: v.string() }`\n   - **Returns:** None (implicit `void`)\n   - **Auth:** Required (throws \"Not authenticated\" if no identity)\n   - **Behavior:** Patches only provided fields; finds user by token identifier\n\n---\n\n### **app/convex/stars.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`getStarredThemes`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ userId: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Array of theme documents (up to 50), filtered by visibility\n   - **Auth:** Optional (checks auth but doesn't require it)\n   - **Field Filtering:** Returns full theme objects BUT only includes themes that are either:\n     - `theme.isPublic === true`, OR\n     - `theme.authorId === currentUserId` (viewer is the author)\n   - **Index:** `by_user_and_theme` (filtered to `userId`, takes 50)\n\n---\n\n### **app/convex/themes.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`getByAuthor`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ authorId: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Array of theme documents (up to 50)\n   - **Auth:** Optional (checks auth but doesn't require it)\n   - **Field Filtering:** \n     - If viewer is the author: returns ALL themes (including private ones)\n     - If viewer is NOT the author: returns only public themes (`.filter((t) => t.isPublic)`)\n   - **Index:** `by_author`\n   - **Behavior:** Returns full theme objects with all fields\n\n**Other relevant queries in this file:**\n- **`list`:** Paginated query of public themes ordered by star count\n- **`getBySlug`:** Returns single theme with auth check for private themes\n- **`getBasicInfo`:** Returns only `{ name, slug }` with privacy checks\n- **`search`:** Full-text search on theme names, returns public only"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ec90dcd9-bd24-4490-bfb2-b14990aaa276","uuid":"6a119941-8723-42ab-b9a3-7c88db0a9c0c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:10:19.996Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Quick exploration: Read the following Convex backend files to understand the query signatures and behavior:\n1. app/convex/users.ts - especially getByUsername, getCurrentUser, updateProfile, and get\n2. app/convex/stars.ts - especially getStarredThemes \n3. app/convex/themes.ts - especially getByAuthor\n\nFor each, note the argument types, return types, and any auth requirements or field filtering.","agentId":"a370f4d785f83e056","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary of Convex Backend Files\n\n### **app/convex/users.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`get`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ id: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Object with filtered fields: `{ _id, username, displayName, avatarUrl }` or `null`\n   - **Auth:** None required (public read)\n\n2. **`getByUsername`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ username: v.string() }`\n   - **Returns:** Full user document (no filtering shown) or `null` (uses `.unique()`)\n   - **Auth:** None required\n   - **Index:** `by_username`\n\n3. **`getCurrentUser`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{}` (no arguments)\n   - **Returns:** Full user document or `null`\n   - **Auth:** Required (checks `ctx.auth.getUserIdentity()`)\n   - **Behavior:** Returns authenticated user's data via token identifier\n\n4. **`updateProfile`** (mutation)\n   - **Args:** `{ displayName?: v.string(), bio?: v.string(), avatarUrl?: v.string() }`\n   - **Returns:** None (implicit `void`)\n   - **Auth:** Required (throws \"Not authenticated\" if no identity)\n   - **Behavior:** Patches only provided fields; finds user by token identifier\n\n---\n\n### **app/convex/stars.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`getStarredThemes`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ userId: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Array of theme documents (up to 50), filtered by visibility\n   - **Auth:** Optional (checks auth but doesn't require it)\n   - **Field Filtering:** Returns full theme objects BUT only includes themes that are either:\n     - `theme.isPublic === true`, OR\n     - `theme.authorId === currentUserId` (viewer is the author)\n   - **Index:** `by_user_and_theme` (filtered to `userId`, takes 50)\n\n---\n\n### **app/convex/themes.ts**\n\n**Key queries:**\n\n1. **`getByAuthor`** (query)\n   - **Args:** `{ authorId: v.id(\"users\") }`\n   - **Returns:** Array of theme documents (up to 50)\n   - **Auth:** Optional (checks auth but doesn't require it)\n   - **Field Filtering:** \n     - If viewer is the author: returns ALL themes (including private ones)\n     - If viewer is NOT the author: returns only public themes (`.filter((t) => t.isPublic)`)\n   - **Index:** `by_author`\n   - **Behavior:** Returns full theme objects with all fields\n\n**Other relevant queries in this file:**\n- **`list`:** Paginated query of public themes ordered by star count\n- **`getBySlug`:** Returns single theme with auth check for private themes\n- **`getBasicInfo`:** Returns only `{ name, slug }` with privacy checks\n- **`search`:** Full-text search on theme names, returns public only"}],"totalDurationMs":8808,"totalTokens":20571,"totalToolUseCount":3,"u